    {
      "id": "94",
      "name": "会話内容",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Ver.5.4限定イベント「三川遊芸夢綺譚」の任務「始夜・夢入るが如く」進行中",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(55, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "トーマ：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "「最高の遊芸」と評されるには、今の完成度じゃ物足りないな…もう少し仕掛けを増やしてみるか？",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(55, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "一つ目小僧：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "トーマの親分の言うとおりにすれば間違いなし！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(55, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "妖狐：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "トーマの親分まじやべぇ！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(55, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "河童：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "さすがトーマの親分！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(55, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "「証城」：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "トーマのオヤヌン！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/27/224893084/c8cf5f1d066762940d52fa3099ecc413_1074922886616721097.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Ver.5.4限定イベント「三川遊芸夢綺譚」の任務「後夜・露水に逢うが如く」開始後",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(55, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "トーマ：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "…君たち、大丈夫か？後遺症とか、残ってないよな？",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(55, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "妖狐：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
